R scripts for making components of Figure 4 Dreos et al. (PLoS Comput Biol. 2021)

Input files:

ATAC-seq footprints

   dm6_c1_atac_enr.txt
   dm6_c2_atac_enr.txt
   dm6_c3_atac_enr.txt
   hg19_c1_atac_enr.txt
   hg19_c2_atac_enr.txt
   hg19_c3_atac_enr.txt

Scripts:

Script to generate components of Figure 4 in PDF fromat 

   fig4.R (Usage Rscript --vanilla fig4.R)

Output files:

ATAC-seq footprints

   fig4_dm6_atac_seq_long.pdf
   fig4_hg19_atac_seq_long.pdf
   fig4_atac_seq_short_dpe.pdf
 
Correlation matrix:

   fig4_atac_correlation_matrix.pdf 
